The paper deals with optimization problems related to wireless communication systems, which are typically studied in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The use of beamforming techniques and cooperative relays suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. The numerical experiments and optimization techniques used in the paper may also be relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
